description: I told Sabrina that if she comes back again to WB, that I'll make it harder than the first time. While not batting an eyelash, she ask where to sign up. So while the first shoot together was pretty good, this one was even better! The suspension in scene two was one of the coolest and hardest I've done in a while. I push her hard. She pushes herself hard. And that adds up to a hot update. Check it out for yourself.
title: Sabrina Fox Returns!
